    schema:courseSchedule <https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/595040067/2025-26/eventSchedule> ;
    schema:description "Enrolling in this course will involve participating in a project cooperating in international teams composed of students from other foreign universities. The project work will be organised in an online phase, followed by a so-called physical week, which will take place at one of the participating universities. Students are expected to participate in both parts and will therefore travel and stay abroad for one week. Although the Erasmus+ programme may provide funding for this, students may have to cover some of these costs."@es ;
